   712	
   713	- `seed_evaluate_task(store, *, base_sha, metrics_schema, slug="demo",
   714	  artifacts_dir=None) -> tuple[task_id, trial_id, proposal_id]`:
   715	  builds a ready proposal + an implement task + drives the trial
   716	  to `status="starting"` with a `commit_sha` set + creates an
   717	  evaluate task. Used by all five evaluator tests.
   718	
   719	The existing chunk-9c fixtures (`bare_repo`, `base_sha`,
   720	`make_child_commit`, `_TEST_IDENTITY`) are reused as-is; the
   721	evaluator does NOT depend on `bare_repo` for its own routes (the
