   725	
   726	The evaluator tests use the existing `signed_in_client` fixture
   727	(no `repo` requirement) ŌĆö they do not need `signed_in_impl_client`.
   728	
   729	## ┬¦J What doesn't change
   730	
   731	- `eden-storage`: nothing.
   732	- `eden-wire`: nothing.
   733	- `eden-dispatch`: nothing.
   734	- `eden-git`: nothing.
   735	- `eden_evaluator_host` (the scripted host): nothing.
